Hello Sue,

I think that 4.25 hours is in "decimal hours,"  which means that 4 and 1/4 hour  (because 
0.25 is 1/4).  So, 4.25 hours would be 4 hours and 15 minutes.

4:25 means 4 hours and 25 minutes


